</UL>

<P>
Criteria Pollutants, established by the EPA, are carbon monoxide, sulfur dioxide, nitrogen dioxide, lead, respirable particulate matter and ozone.
<P>
<I>Source: Texas Air Control Board, </I>Air Quality in Texas: 1992 and Beyond, <I>(Austin: TACB, 1993), 4.</I>
<P>



<P><P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../line.gif" ALT="Line" WIDTH="100%"></CENTER><p>
