</TD><TD>
<FONT COLOR="F3C228"><H4><FONT SIZE=+2>A</FONT> B O U T<BR>
the <FONT SIZE=+2>S</FONT> P E A K E R</FONT>
</TD></TR>
</TABLE><BR>

<IMG SRC="./graphics/speaker.gif" ALT="Angus Ma" WIDTH=222 HEIGHT=327 BORDER=0 ALIGN=right>
Angus Ma holds a B.Eng. from Queen's University, an M.Eng. from Carleton
University and an M.B.A. from the University of Ottawa.  He began his
career as a software designer for Northern Telecom and Bell-Northern
Research in Ottawa. After leaving NT/BNR, he developed micro-to-mainframe
products and UNIX based office automation systems.  In 1986, he started AHM
Technology Corporation, which provides network design, analysis and
troubleshooting services to large corporate clients.  In addition Mr. Ma
lectures frequently throughout North America, Europe and Asia. He is a
technical editor for "Learning Tree International" and the author of two of
their popular network courses.  Mr. Ma has worked in data and
telecommunications since 1980 and has extensive practical experience in
planning, maintaining and troubleshooting LAN/WAN <A NAME="WG">internetworks.</A>

<BR><BR><BR><BR>
<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0>
<TR><TD ALIGN=left VALIGN=top>
<IMG SRC="./graphics/bullet.gif" WIDTH=75 HEIGHT=36 BORDER=0>
</TD><TD>
<FONT COLOR="F3C228"><H4><FONT SIZE=+2>W</FONT> A N D E L&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=+2>&</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE=+2>G</FONT> O L T E R M A N N</FONT>
</TD></TR>
</TABLE><BR>

Wandel & Goltermann, a premier supplier of communications test solutions,
provides network performance, analysis and management solutions to leading
companies around the world.  Wandel & Goltermann Internetwork
Troubleshooting tools possess an industry wide reputation for power,
flexibility, and cost-effectiveness.  This is evidenced by Cisco's
selection of the Wandel & Goltermann Domino as an integral component of
their toolkit used in supporting their world-wide customer base.  Wandel &
Goltermann Dominos have also won the Data Communications magazine Hot
Products award and are emerging as a 'next generation' troubleshooting
tool.  Wandel & Goltermann LAN/WAN Troubleshooting Tools - improving
networks <A NAME="Register"></A>world-wide.

