<TITLE>What we're all About...</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY>

<BODY BACKGROUND="./gifs/pbbckgnd.gif" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><BASEFONT SIZE=4>



<CENTER>

<H1><B>P.B. FRASER & ASSOCIATES</B><BR>

<IMG SRC="./gifs/pbicon.gif" WIDTH=51 HEIGHT=46 ALIGN=left><IMG SRC="./gifs/pbicon.gif" WIDTH=51 HEIGHT=46 ALIGN=right>Financial Strategies Group</H1>

</CENTER>



<TABLE BORDER=10 CELLPADDING=10 CELLSPACING=10>

<TR><TD>

<H2><I>Our Mission</I>

</TD></TR>

<TR><TD>

<H3>We at P.B. Fraser & Associates are a team of independent Financial Strategists dedicated to the process of understanding and fulfilling the needs of our clients in a spirit of caring and excellence.  Our commitment to working together and fostering each other's personal and professional development enhances our ability to serve our clients.  It is our purpose to assist in the creation of an exciting future for everyone who comes in contact with our group.

</TD></TR>

<TR><TD>

<CENTER><H2>...Thinking Outside the Box

</TD></TR>

<TR><TD>

<H2><I>Our Vision:</I></H2>


<H3>Over the next five years, we will strive to be...<BR>



<P><IMG SRC="./gifs/pbicon.gif" WIDTH=51 HEIGHT=46 ALIGN=left>a team giving back to the community,</P><BR>



<P><IMG SRC="./gifs/pbicon.gif" WIDTH=51 HEIGHT=46 ALIGN=left>the holders and operators of the finest systems available for optimal profitability so that every stakeholder of our organization benefits on an ever-increasing scale,</P>



<P><IMG SRC="./gifs/pbicon.gif" WIDTH=51 HEIGHT=46 ALIGN=left>a financial practice of such quality that we would become the standard of excellence in our industry.</P>

</TD></TR>

</TABLE>



