<CENTER>
<H1><B>P.B. FRASER & ASSOCIATES</B><BR>
<IMG SRC="./gifs/pbicon.gif" WIDTH=51 HEIGHT=46 ALIGN=left><IMG SRC="./gifs/pbicon.gif" WIDTH=51 HEIGHT=46 ALIGN=right>Financial Strategies Group</H1>
</CENTER>


<TABLE BORDER=10 CELLPADDING=10 CELLSPACING=10>
<TR><TD COLSPAN=3 ALIGN=middle>
<H1>Comprehensive Financial Planning
</TD></TR>
<TR><TD COLSPAN=3>
<H2><I>What we do for you...</I>
</TD></TR>
<TR><TD COLSPAN=3>
<H3>At P. B. Fraser & Associates we strive to provide our clients with the education they need to make informed decisions for their future.  Our commitment as dedicated teachers gives our clients people they can count on to help them build successful financial strategies.
</TD></TR>
<TR><TD COLSPAN=3></TD></TR>
<TR><TD COLSPAN=3>
<H2><I>What you can expect...</I>
</TD></TR>
<TR><TD COLSPAN=3>
<H3>Every client of P. B. Fraser & Associates has the opportunity to receive a comprehensive financial analysis.  This integrates all aspects of their financial affairs to ensure a focused approach to achieving their future plans.
</TD></TR>
<TR><TD COLSPAN=3></TD></TR>
<TR><TD>
<H2><I>Relationships not just for today...</I>
</TD><TD>
<H2><I>Services...</I>
</TD><TD>
<H2><I>Products...</I>
</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>
<H3>Regular reviews are an integral part of our services.  It is imperative to look at progress periodically to ensure everything is on the right track.  Also, as needs change, it is important to have on-going information in all areas of personal fiscal management.  These areas include:
</TD><TD>
<I><B><P><IMG SRC="./gifs/pbicon2.gif" WIDTH=41 HEIGHT=33 ALIGN=left>Charitable Gifting<BR>and Estate Planning</P>
