<H5>
<P>"Thinking Outside the Box" is produced by P. B. Fraser and Associates as an information service with the understanding that it does not render financial accounting, legal or other professional advice. The commentary contained herein is not intended, nor should it be relied upon, to replace  specific professional advice. It is recommended that readers consult their professional advisors regarding any matter addressed in this publication. Errors and omissions excepted.</P>
</H5>

