<CENTER><H1>Electronic Service</H1></CENTER>
<CENTER><H1>Monitor Repair</H1></CENTER>
<CENTER><H1>Computer Maintenance</H1></CENTER>
<CENTER><H2>Beau Video -  #7 Unit B, Hamilton Avenue North, Ottawa, Ontario</H2></CENTER>
<CENTER><H2>Tel: (613) 860-0305</H2></CENTER>
<HR SIZE=2>
<P></P>
<TABLE BORDER="0"><TR><TD COLSTART="1"><IMG
ALIGN="TOP" SRC="./gifs/curie2.gif" HSPACE="30"></TD><TD COLSTART="2"><P>Beau
Video has been a provider of quality electronic repair services for over 15
years. Our well equipped shop features <B>state of the art analyzing equipment</B>:</P>
<UL>
<LI> Signal Generator to resolve any monitor format (Hercules, PGC, Apollo,
Radius, XGA-2 and more)
</LI>
<LI> Component Analyzer to check the integrity of all specifications
</LI>
<LI> Tube Restoration Equipment to restore any tube to the manufacturer's
specifications</LI>
</UL>
<P>We do <I>upgrading</I>, <I>configuration</I>, <I>installation</I> and
<I>repairs</I>, all with a flat rate labour charge. No video or monitor problem
is too tough for our well trained service technicians. </P>
<P>So next time you have a <B>video, monitor or electronic repair problem</B>,
take it to <B>Beau Video</B>, Ottawa's electronic service expert.</P>
