<H2>About the Author</H2>

<P>Kathleen M. Gow is a sociologist, mental health
specialist, author and a member of the Centre's Research Council.  She
received a Bachelor of Arts degree and Master of Social Work from the
University of Toronto, and a PhD. in Sociology at York University.  Dr. Gow
was awarded the Canada Foundation Scholarship for post-graduate work at
the Tavistock Clinic for Children and Families in London, England, an
institution famous for its work in the field of children, families, and
education.  Dr. Gow is the author of Yes Virginia, There is Right and
Wrong!<BR>

