<H2><I>Chris L. Johnson</I><BR><BR>
<IMG SRC="./gifs/chris.gif" ALT="Picture of Chris Johnson" WIDTH=200 HEIGHT=200 HSPACE=0 ALIGN=top><BR><BR>
<I>Asset Manager/Financial Planner</I><BR>
<H3><P>"The greatest service I can provide you is to listen carefully.  Then I can understand your goals and concerns, and furnish strategies to enhance your financial future and your quality of life."
</TD><TD ROWSPAN=5 VALIGN=top>
<H3>
<P><IMG SRC="./gifs/pbicon2.gif" WIDTH=41 HEIGHT=33 ALIGN=baseline>Chris Johnson is a Bachelor of Commerce graduate from Ottawa University.  He is a native of Montreal and specializes in the area of asset management.  Having completed the Canadian Securities Course, he is particularly attuned to the equity markets, bond markets and mutual fund investing.  Chris believes that the key to safe, reasonable growth of your money is a properly diversified collection of investments.</P>

