<IMG SRC="./gifs/lloyd.gif" ALT="Picture of Lloyd Wade" WIDTH=200 HEIGHT=200 HSPACE=0 ALIGN=top><BR><BR>
<I>Financial Planner</I><BR>
<H3><P>"Most of us, I am sure, have had to cope with daily financial demands, perhaps raising a family at the same time, with a concerned eye to the future, whether education, new home, retirement, or any other personal goal.  I am committed to listening, understanding, teaching, and working in partnership with our clients in developing a comprehensive strategy toward realizing their dreams."
</TD><TD ROWSPAN=5 VALIGN=top>
<H3>
<P><IMG SRC="gifs/pbicon2.gif" WIDTH=41 HEIGHT=33 ALIGN=baseline>Lloyd is a Certified Management Accountant, and joined our office after a long and varied career in telecommunications - both in Canada and internationally.  His career spanned not only Accounting, but International Marketing and Human Resources.  His giant leap to financial planning arose from a desire to teach and help our clients develop a financial roadmap for their future.  He is committed to creating a long-term bond with our clients, working together toward realizing their financial ambitions.</P>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="./gifs/pbfraser.gif" WIDTH=263 HEIGHT=239></CENTER>

<P>Lloyd is married with five grown children, and lives in Orleans.  He strongly believes in giving back to the community, through a variety of roles within the accounting profession, as well as being an active volunteer with a local hospital and other charitable ventures.
