<HEAD>
<TITLE>Peter B. Fraser in Detail...</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BACKGROUND="./gifs/pbbckgnd.gif" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><BASEFONT SIZE=4>

<TABLE BORDER=10 CELLPADDING=5 CELLSPACING=10>
<TR><TD ALIGN=middle>

<H2><I>Peter B. Fraser</I><BR><BR>
<IMG SRC="./gifs/peter.gif" ALT="Picture of Peter Fraser" WIDTH=200 HEIGHT=200 HSPACE=0 ALIGN=top><BR><BR>
<I>President</I><BR>
<H3><P>"My personal commitment is to establish a lifetime relationship as a trusted financial coach, assisting you towards a safe, secure and prosperous future."
</TD><TD ROWSPAN=5>
<H4>
<IMG SRC="./gifs/pbicon2.gif" WIDTH=41 HEIGHT=33 ALIGN=baseline><I>Peter Fraser is...</I><BR>

<BR>An Honours Commerce graduate from Guelph University in 1982.
<BR>A member, Canadian Association of Financial Planners.
<BR>A member, Life Underwriters Association of Canada.
<BR>Owner and President of P.B. Fraser & Associates.
<BR>A financial guest on CBC radio, published in The Ottawa Citizen and other area newspapers, popular speaker at workshops.<BR><BR>

<I>Peter Fraser is...</I>

<P>Married to Heather (since 1983). Together they are raising three sons. He and Heather are both very involved in the private school attended by their children.  Peter is active in his church, especially in the area of stewardship, and he serves on the Board of Directors for a local Crisis Centre. Peter also enjoys walking, golfing, swimming and reading.</P>

<I>Peter Solves...</I>

<P>Estate Planning Problems: Today, more than ever, governments at all levels are preparing to seriously encroach on estates after death. Costly financial mistakes need not be your legacy; Peter will identify the most effective strategies for you.</P>

<P>Retirement Planning Problems: We are living longer and facing the twin evils of taxation and inflation. These issues seriously impact the likelihood of a prosperous retirement. Peter creates futures that ensure you won't run out of money before you run out of life.</P>

<P>Downsizing/Severance Management: Persons taking early retirement packages are receiving more money at one time than they have ever before. Peter helps you safely and carefully take full advantage of these funds. At P. B. Fraser & Associates we strive to provide our clients with the education they need to make informed decisions for their future.  Peter's commitment as a dedicated teacher gives his clients a representative they can count on to help them build successful financial futures.</P>

<P>Every client of P. B. Fraser & Associates has the opportunity to receive a comprehensive financial analysis.  This integrates all aspects of their financial affairs to ensure a focused approach to achieving their future plans.</P>

<P>Regular reviews are an integral part of our services.  It is imperative to look at progress periodically to ensure everything is on the right track.  Also, as needs change, it is important to have on-going information in all areas of personal financial management.</P>
</TD></TR>
