<HEAD>
<TITLE>You Asked - We Listened!</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><BASEFONT SIZE=4>

<A HREF="./jan_p1.html"> <B><H1>... Thinking Outside the Box</B>
<BR><I>Issue #1 - January 1996</I></H1></A>
<H2>P. B. FRASER & ASSOCIATES<BR>
Financial Strategies Group</H2>
<HR SIZE=4>
<H1><I>You Asked - We Listened!</I>
<HR WIDTH=75% ALIGN=left SIZE=8 NOSHADE></H1>
<H4>By Greta N. Luimes</H4><BR>

<P>As financial planners at P. B. Fraser & Associates, we continually encourage our clients to tell us their
feelings on what we do right for them, as well as what can be improved upon. One of the recurring concerns we heard during 1995 was a wish to have more direct access to a wider range of products. More
than ever before, the average Canadian understands, at an instinctive level, that it's important to diversify
one's personal assets. As a result, people are looking with a more inquisitive and critical eye at what's
available in the financial marketplace. Mutual funds, guaranteed investment certificates and insurance
products have been relatively easy for us to provide. We have long recognized that access to bonds and
stocks is also important.</P>

<P>We are pleased to have taken some bold steps to service your needs. These are only first steps, and
many more are planned for development during the next few months.</P>

<P><B>Bonds-</B> Through our licencing dealer, we have entered into a strategic affiliation with the brokerage firm Levesque Beaubien Geoffrion, which is owned by the National Bank. We now have on-line access to current bond pricing throughout the trading day. Beginning now, you can buy strip-bonds, provincial and government of Canada long-term bonds over $20,000 within self-directed RSP's. Other fixed income products and bond purchases for open accounts will be available in the near future.</P>

<P><B>Stocks-</B> We are involved in the incorporation of a new management company which will serve to provide our financial planners with the tools necessary to be involved in the purchase and sale of stocks. A Vice-President of Research has been hired to develop this market for your availability. Further news will
be forthcoming in the next few months. The benefits to this will be the:</P>

<P>*  direct purchase of stocks for your portfolios, and<BR>
*  discretionary portfolio management.</P>

<P>We are proud to be affiliated with a group as progressive as Balanced Planning. The opportunity to have input into their plans is something we value greatly because this input comes from YOU. Thank you for
your continued support of P. B. Fraser & Associates and for your frankness and candor in sharing your
advice and concerns.</P>

<HR SIZE=4>

