<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Directions to P.B. Fraser & Associates</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><BASEFONT SIZE=4>

<CENTER>
<H1><B>P.B. FRASER & ASSOCIATES</B>
<BR><IMG SRC="./gifs/pbicon.gif" WIDTH=51 HEIGHT=46 ALIGN=left><IMG SRC="./gifs/pbicon.gif" WIDTH=51 HEIGHT=46 ALIGN=right>Financial Strategies Group</H1>
<HR SIZE=4>

<IMG SRC="./gifs/pb1.jpg" ALT="Map with Directions to P. B. Fraser & Associates">
<H1>Easy Access to P.B. Fraser & Associates...
</CENTER><IMG SRC="./gifs/pbfraser.gif" ALT="P.B. Fraser & Associates Logo" WIDTH=263 HEIGHT=239 ALIGN=right></H1>

<BR><H2>Travelling <I>East</I> on HW#417 (Queensway)...</H2>

<P>Take the "<B>Carling West</B>" exit and turn <I>left</I> onto <B>Kirkwood</B>.  After passing underneath the Queensway, turn <I>right</I> on <B>Carling</B> (going east).  Then turn <I>right</I> again on <B>Meath</B> Street.  Just passing the <B>Embassy West Hotel</B> on the right, P.B. Fraser & Associates is your next <I>right</I> at 824 Meath St. across from the <B>Talisman Hotel</B>.</P>

<BR><H2>Travelling <I>West</I> on HW#417 (Queensway)...</H2>

<P>Take the "<B>Carling East</B>" exit and keep driving past <B>Kirkwood</B> until you see the <B>Embassy West Hotel</B> or <B>Meath</B> St. and turn <I>right</I>.  Straight across from the <B>Talisman Hotel</B> (on your left) is P.B. Fraser & Associates on your <I>right</I>. (824 Meath St.)</P>

<HR SIZE=4>

