<HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2>
<A NAME="system"><H3><FONT SIZE=+1><FONT color="#EE0000">System Requirements</FONT></FONT></H3></A>

<U><FONT SIZE=+1>For optimum performance, we recommend the following system:</FONT></U>
<br>
<U><FONT SIZE=+1>IBM PC platform</FONT></U>
<UL type=disc>
<LI>486 processor or faster 
<LI>8mb RAM or larger
<LI>VGA color monitor 
<LI>Dial-up modem, 28.8 kpbs or higher 
</UL>
<br>
<U><FONT SIZE=+1>MACINTOSH platform</FONT></U>
<UL type=disc>
<LI>System 7.0 or above 
<LI>8mb RAM or higher
<LI>Dial-up modem, 28.8 kpbs or higher 
</UL>


<U><A NAME="software"><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE=+1><FONT color="#EE0000">Pickup your <EM><STRONG>Talaya Suite</STRONG></EM></FONT></FONT></A></U><BR> 
<A NAME="suite"></A>
<CENTER><TABLE COLSPEC="L20" BORDER=3 WIDTH=450 CELLPADDING=5>
<TR><TD><STRONG><FONT SIZE=+1>Talaya Internet Suite </FONT></STRONG> (PC) is a customized 
version of the latest Netscape Navigator with email, dialer, Registration Wizard, and Netscape Installation Guide.  Talaya Suite is available at IT&E's Talaya 2000 Customer Service Center or participating vendors such as Dimension Systems, Mesa Computer Systems& Services, JJ Computers, MicroAge, Computer USA or Webscape on Guam, or at IT&E Saipan located in the Sablan Building in San Jose.
<br><br>For Macintosh users, please proceed to the IT&E office closest to you.
</TD></TR>
</TABLE></CENTER><BR>

