<A NAME="new"></A><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><LI><STRONG><FONT color="#EE0000">Opening A New Account</FONT></STRONG><BR><BR>
Sign up for a Talaya account at any IT&E office or at participating vendors such as Dimension Systems, MicroAge, JJ Computer, Mesa Computer Systems & Services, Webscape or Computer USA on <b>Guam</b>, or at IT&E <b>Saipan</b> located in the Sablan Building in San Jose, telephone 234-8521.<BR><BR>
	
<HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><LI><STRONG><FONT color="#EE0000">Applicable Fees </FONT> - personal accounts</STRONG><BR><BR>
A one time <STRONG>Set Up Charge</STRONG> of $29.00 includes the Talaya Suite with the installation and operating instructions plus 5 bonus hours.  A <STRONG>Minimum Monthly Charge</STRONG> also applies based on the service plan selected.  For a complete look at the various plans available, please see <A HREF="#pricing">Monthly Service Plans</A><BR>

<BR><LI><STRONG><FONT color="#EE0000">Applicable Fees</FONT> - business accounts</STRONG><BR><BR>
A one time <STRONG>Set Up Charge</STRONG> of $25.00 includes the Talaya Suite with the installation and operating instructions plus 5 bonus hours.  A <STRONG>Minimum Monthly Charge</STRONG> also applies based on the service plan selected.  For a complete look at the various plans available, please see <A HREF="#pricing">Monthly Service Plans</A><BR></UL>


<A NAME="pro"></A><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><LI><STRONG><FONT color="#EE0000">Changing Service Plans</FONT></STRONG><BR><BR>

Talaya Users wishing to change their current Service Plans to fit their needs are requested to visit any of our IT&E offices on Guam, IT&E Saipan in the Sablan Building in San Jose and complete a request form. Users may change their plan at anytime during the month up until the 25th of that month.
 Any change requests after the 25th, all will take effect the suceeding month .<BR><BR>
For a complete look at the various plans available, please see <A HREF="#pricing">Monthly Service Plans</A><BR><BR><BR>

<A NAME="webspace"><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><LI><STRONG><FONT color="#EE0000">Webspace Publishing</FONT><STRONG></A><BR><BR>
<TABLE WIDTH=450 ALIGN=center BORDER><TR>
Web Space Rate Plans are available for personal or commercial accounts wishing to publish on the Web to appeal to Guam, Saipan, The Pacific Region, or the entire free world.<BR>
<TR>
<TD ALIGN=center><STRONG>Rate<BR>Plans</STRONG></TD>
