<A NAME="pay"></A><H2><EM>Payment of Long Distance Bills</EM></H2>
<CENTER><TABLE COLSPEC="L20" BORDER=0 WIDTH=500 CELLPADDING=0>
<TR><TD>
IT&E makes this process as convenient as possible by having several locations available for making payments throughout Guam and Saipan. Or simply send your payment through the mail using the self-addressed envelopes provided with each billing statement received.</TD></TR>
</TABLE></CENTER><BR>

