<TITLE>
LOA Information
</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="ffffff" background="backgrounds/paper12l.jpg" TEXT="000000" LINK="0000FF" VLINK="000080" ALINK="0000FF">

<h1>Letter of Agency (LOA) Information</h1>

The LOA authorizes IT&E to act as an agent on your behalf for the sole purpose of presubscribing 
your telephone number(s) to IT&E for long distance service.
<br>
<br>

<UL>
<LI>Only the official GTA subscriber shall sign the LOA form.
<LI>One LOA is required for each billing address. Separate LOA must be submitted
for each additional billing address indicating the telephone number(s).
</UL>

<br>

<A HREF="loa.htm">Click here for the Letter of Agency (LOA) form.</A>

<hr>
<center>
<A HREF="faq.htm">Frequently Asked Questions</A> 
| <FONT COLOR=808080>Letter of Agency Information</FONT> 
| <A HREF="loa.htm">Letter of Agency</A>
| <A HREF="promotions.htm">Promotions</A>
</center>
<br>

</BODY>
</HTML>
