<center>

<h2><strong>LETTER OF AGENCY</strong></h2>

</center>

<br>

<br>

I hereby select IT&E Overseas, Inc. as my Primary Interexchange Carrier (PIC) by GTA and authorize IT&E Overseas, Inc.

to act as an Agent on my behalf for the sole purpose of presubscribing my entire account to IT&E for the following telephone

number(s):

<br>

<br>

<center>


<FORM METHOD=POST action="http://www2.ite.net/cgi-bin/loa.cgi">
