<input type=text size=20 name=telephones17>
</td>
<td>
<input type=text size=20 name=telephones18>
</td>

</TABLE>


</center>

<br>

<br>

Furthermore, I understand that only one Interexchange Carrier (IXC) may be designated as my interstate PIC for 

any one telephone number.  I also understand and accept that any PIC selection I make may involve a charge

to me if I change my chosen PIC after conversion.

<br>

<br>
