<BR>
<BR>
<hr width=95% align=center>
<font size=-1><strong>What's New in Kids' World?  Well virtually everything on the Kids' World is new!  We've renovated this world to something cooler. We've Updated links and of course added new ones for your viewing pleasure.  Put cool news graphics in it and now divided it into cool new categories. 
</font></strong>

<hr width=95% align=center>

<font size=-1><strong>
First thing you kids should check out is the <a href="rules.htm">Online Rules</a>.  These are just basic rules that every kid should follow while they are on the net. Basically the first rule we have for you is JUST HAVE FUN! (without getting in trouble that is).
<hr width=95% align=center>

 Then you should zoom in to the <a href="kidgrab.htm">Grab Bag</a> page.  This is newest attraction in the Kids' World because it's full of fun interactive stuffs.  Here we will show the best places on the web to join a contest..Play interactive games or just learn something new.

<hr width=95% align=center>

Now the Kids' World page is divided into different cool categories now.  I suggest you check each page that interests you the most. And then check the others.  Just have fun!

<hr width=95% align=center>
