International Soccer Server</a> - Statistics.<BR>
<a href="http://www.cybergoal.com/soccer">Kid's Soccer Home Page</a> - Soccer made fun for the web. Database searches for worldwide soccer websites, soccer penpals, chat soccer meetings, newsgoups and animations.<BR>
<a href="http://www.opel.com/opel/english/sports/index.html">Opel Sports</a> - info on the european soccer championship 1996<BR>
<a href="http://web-usa.com/soccer/">Planet Soccer</a> - Everything and anything about Soccer...<BR>
<a href="http://www.atm.ch.cam.ac.uk/sports/games.html">Soccer Games</a>  - Soccer related game software for PCs.<BR>
<a href="http://www.soccernews.com/">Soccer NewsNet</a><BR>
<a href="http://www.sportsnetwork.com/soccer/soccer.html">Soccer Page [The Sports Network]</a><BR>
<a href="http://www.tiac.net/users/tmac/index.html">SoccerCoach!</a> - Forum for soccer coaches to exchange information on drills, jobs, results and anything that affects heir teams and their jobs.<BR>
<a href="http://www.csn.net/~eid/soccer/sccrindx.html">SoccerNews OnLine</a> - Headquarters for US National Teams, MLS, USISL, A-League, CISL, NPSL, International Competitions<BR>
<a href="http://www.fifa.com/index.html">Federation Internationale de Football Association (FIFA)</a> - FIFA is the world's governing body for football/soccer.<BR>
<a href="http://www.wpe.com/~nshof/">National Soccer Hall of Fame</a><BR>
<a href="http://www.serve.com/soccer/">New River Valley Soccer Referee Association</a> - information about soccer refereeing, certification information, contact people, field  locations, links to referee-related sites.<BR>
<a href="http://www.sleague.com.sg/">S.League Soccer</a> - official Singapore Professional Soccer League site with the latest results, player profiles, and  football news.<BR>
<a href="http://users.aol.com/socfed/">United States Soccer Federation</a> - The official home page.<BR>
<a href="http://www.cris.com/~Jg189/wsf/">Women's Soccer Foundation</a>
 - Soccer for girls and women: news, events, contacts, and links.<BR>

<BR><BR><CENTER>...And dont forget to come back to the Talaya 2000 Sports Pages...</CENTER><BR><BR>

