version of Netscape Navigator 1.22, Eudora Light email 1.5.2, Dialer, Registration Wizard, and Netscape Installation Guide.  Talaya Suite is available at IT&E's Talaya 2000 Customer Service Center or participating vendors such as MEGAbyte, UBIX, Dimension Systems, MicroAge, Computer World, Computer USA or Hyper, Inc.</TD></TR>
</TABLE></CENTER><BR>

