<A NAME="new"></A><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><LI><STRONG><FONT color="#EE0000">Opening A New Account</FONT></STRONG><BR><BR>

Sign up for a Talaya account at our Talaya 2000 Customer Service Center IT&E 	Tamuning Office, 1st Floor Annex), telephone number 646-INET, or at participating vendors such as MEGAbyte, UBIX, Dimension Systems, MicroAge, Computer World, or Computer USA.<BR>
	
<UL><LH><STRONG><FONT color="#EE0000">Applicable Fees</FONT></STRONG></LH> <BR>
A one time <STRONG>Set Up Charge</STRONG> of $29.00 includes the Talaya Suite with the installation and operating instructions plus 5 bonus hours.  A <STRONG>Minimum Monthly Charge</STRONG> also applies based on the service plan selected.  For a complete look at the various plans available, please see <A HREF="#pricing">Monthly Service Plans</A><BR></UL>

<A NAME="pro"></A><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><LI><STRONG><FONT color="#EE0000">Changing Service Plans</FONT></STRONG><BR><BR>

Talaya Users wishing to change their current Service Plans to fit their needs are 	requested to visit our Talaya Customer Service Center (IT&E Tamuning Office, 1st Floor Annex) and complete a request form. Users may change their plan at 	anytime during the month.<BR><BR>
For a complete look at the various plans available, please see <A HREF="#pricing">Monthly Service Plans</A><BR><BR><BR>

<A NAME="suite"></A><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><LI><STRONG><FONT color="#EE0000">Purchasing the Talaya Suite</FONT></STRONG><BR><BR>

	The Talaya Suite is a customized version of Netscape Navigator 1.22, Eudora Light email 1.5.2, Dialer, Registration Wizard, and Netscape Installation Guide.<BR><BR>
	Talaya Users who are utilizing a third-party software and wish to obtain the Talaya Suite may purchase the suite by visiting the Talaya Customer Service Center (IT&E Tamuning Office, 1st floor Annex) and complete the purchase request.  The cost for the suite is $29.00 which includes 5 bonus hours.<BR><BR>
Talaya Suite is also available at participating vendors such as MEGAbyte, UBIX, Dimension Systems, MicroAge, Computer World, or Computer USA.<BR><BR>
For new accounts, the Talaya Suite is included with the one time setup 	charge which comes with 5 bonus hours.<BR><BR>


