<A NAME="services"><H2><STRONG><FONT color="#EE0000">Talaya 2000 Services</FONT></STRONG></H2></A>
 
<STRONG><EM><A NAME="email">E-Mail</A></EM></STRONG> 
<UL type=disc>
<LI>The Internet's most popular application, reduce pesky paperwork, communicate with other users globally.
</UL>
<STRONG><EM><A NAME="news">News Items</A></EM></STRONG> 
<UL type=disc>
<LI>The latest news, weather and sports.  Be the first to know what's happening worldwide.
</UL> 
<STRONG><EM><A NAME="www">World Wide Web</A></EM></STRONG> 
<UL type=disc>
<LI>Browse through WWW where advertisers market their products and services on a global scale.
</UL> 
<STRONG><EM><A NAME="local">Local Info</A></EM></STRONG> 
<UL type=disc>
<LI>New and useful information on local topics of interest.
</UL>
<STRONG><EM><A NAME="public">Public Services</A> </EM></STRONG> 
<UL type=disc>
<LI>Check out the latest on Gov Guam and other local public services.
</UL> 
<STRONG><EM><A NAME="gopher">Gopher</A></EM></STRONG> 
<UL type=disc>
<LI>Access and retrieve public domain files anywhere on the Internet, do your homework and find facts fast.
</UL> 
<STRONG><EM><A NAME="ftp">File Transfer Protocol</A></EM></STRONG> 
<UL type=disc>
<LI>Download utilities, games, shareware, software updates and other public domain programs.
</UL> 
<STRONG><EM><A NAME="telnet">Telnet/Rlogin</A></EM></STRONG> 
<UL type=disc>
<LI>Remote access other computers via TALAYA 2000.  Access other online services like America Online without long distance or expensive local access fees - just pay regular Talaya online time!
</UL>
