</td><td>
<table border=0><td>
<IMG HSPACE=2 SRC="images/blueball.gif">
<BR><BR><BR>
</td><td>
<A HREF="#CALL ACCOUNTING">Call Accounting and Integrated Systems</A><BR><BR>
<IMG HSPACE=2 SRC="images/blueball.gif"><A HREF="#HOSP">Hospitality Services</A><BR>
<IMG HSPACE=2 SRC="images/blueball.gif"><A HREF="#TABS">TABS - Telephone Accounting and Billing System</A>
</td><tr><td>
<IMG HSPACE=2 SRC="images/blueball.gif"></td><td><A HREF="#VM">VM - Voice Mail / Business Application Systems</A></td></tr><tr><td>
