<IMG HSPACE=2 SRC="images/blueball.gif"></td><td><A HREF="#EQUIPMENT">General Equipment</A>
</td><tr></table>
</td><td></table>
<CENTER><A HREF="talaya.htm"><IMG SRC="images/1homebut.gif" ALT="[HomePage]" WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=32 HSPACE=5 border=none></A><A HREF="itehome.htm"><IMG SRC="images/itebutn.gif" ALT="[IT&E]" WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=32 HSPACE=5 border=none></A><A HREF="mailto:genmgr@ite.net"><IMG SRC="images/mailbutn.gif" ALT="[Contact Us!]" WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=32 HSPACE=5 border=none></A><A HREF="help.htm"><IMG SRC="images/helpbutn.gif" ALT="[Help]" WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=32 HSPACE=5 border=none></A>
<BR>
</center>
<HR WIDTH=80% ALIGN=center SIZE=2>
<A NAME="CALL ACCOUNTING"><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+1>CALL ACCOUNTING AND INTEGRATED SYSTEMS</FONT></A></CENTER><BR>
<BR>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=2 width=90%>
<TD><center><A NAME="FCS"><STRONG>HOSPITALITY SERVICES</STRONG></A></center></TD>
<TR>
</TABLE></CENTER>
<BR>
<UL COMPACT>
<IMG HSPACE=2 SRC="images/blueball.gif"><STRONG><U>DIALINK PMS(Property Management Systems)</U></STRONG>
<P>Automated and fully integrated front office system which provides services including call posting, room status updating, guest check-in & -out and message waiting lamp control.</P>
<IMG HSPACE=2 SRC="images/blueball.gif"><STRONG><U>DIALINK VMS(Voice Mail System)</U></STRONG>
<P>Automated messaging system utilizing multi-language voice prompts and touch-tone control from touch-tone telephones.</P>
<IMG HSPACE=2 SRC="images/blueball.gif"><STRONG><U>DIALINK AWS(Auto Wake-up System)</U></STRONG>
<P>The basic system for guest wake-up calls.</P>
<IMG HSPACE=2 SRC="images/blueball.gif"><STRONG><U>DIALINK VCS(Voice Conference System)</U></STRONG>
<P>Automated system allows users to place requests and updates directly from guest room phones.  The services available range from setting wake-up calls to updating minibar accounts.</P>
<IMG HSPACE=2 SRC="images/blueball.gif"><STRONG><U>DIALINK CAI(Call Accounting Interface)</U></STRONG>
<P>Provides basic front office support, needed for basic guest management such as guest check-in & -out and call posting of long distance calls.</P>
<IMG HSPACE=2 SRC="images/blueball.gif"><STRONG><U>ALPHANET(In-Room Faxing)</U></STRONG>
<P>Provides comprehensive in-room fax service to hotel guests via an ordinary telephone number.  This allows the guest to receive and send faxes directly from thier room without the assistance/intervention from hotel staff.</P>

<HR WIDTH=90% ALIGN=center SIZE=2>
<TABLE WIDTH=90% ALIGN=bleedleft>
<TD><A NAME="TABS"><IMG HSPACE=10 SRC="images/tabs2.gif"></TD>
<TD><FONTSIZE=+1><STRONG>(Telephone Accounting and Billing System)</STRONG></FONT></TD>
<TR>
</TABLE>
<BR>
Designed primarily for business applications the TABS 2000 system is a Call Accounting System that records all out bound calls originating from various extensions.<BR>
<BR>
<A NAME="VM"><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+1>VOICE MAIL SYSTEMS/BUSINESS APPLICATION SYSTEMS</FONT></CENTER></A><BR>
<BR>
<STRONG>Automated Telephone Receptionist</STRONG><BR>
In the business arena, even one missed telephone call can cost a company a bundle. Thats why IT&E offers ' the Automated Telephone Receptionist, a stand alone Software System that interfaces with Key Telephone or PABX Systems.<BR>
<BR>
<STRONG>MITEL VX</STRONG><BR>
Without a solid record of all of those telephone calls you couldnt take because you were either already on the telephone or out of the office. IT&Es fully integrated Voice Mail system, the MITEL VX is specifically designed for MITEL digital PABX systems.<BR>
<BR>

<A NAME="PHONE"><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+1>TELEPHONE SYSTEMS</FONT></A><BR></CENTER>
<CENTER>
<A HREF="mitel.htm"><IMG SRC="images/mitel.gif" BORDER=none ALT="[image]"></A><BR>
<A HREF="samsung.htm"><IMG SRC="images/samsung1.gif" BORDER=none ALT="[image]"></A><BR>
<A HREF="hyundai.htm"><IMG SRC="images/hyundai1.gif" BORDER=none ALT="[image]"><BR></A>
<BR>
<A NAME="ACD"><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+1>AUTOMATIC CALL DISTRIBUTION (ACD) Systems</FONT></A><BR></CENTER>
The Automatic Call Distribution system does exactly what its name says it does. It distributes calls evenly to all agents logged on to the telephone system.<BR>
<BR>
