<HEAD><TITLE>International Direct Dial Service</TITLE>


</HEAD>


<BODY TEXT="#000000" LINK="#000072" VLINK="#000000" ALINK="#700000">


<CENTER><table border=0><tr><td><IMG SRC="images/world2.gif" ALT="[image]"></td><td><FONT  SIZE=+2><CENTER>INTERNATIONAL<BR> DIRECT DIAL SERVICE</CENTER></FONT></td><td>


<IMG SRC="images/world2.gif">


</td></tr></table>


</CENTER>





<BR><BR>





<center>


<table border=0><tr><td>


<CENTER><STRONG>IT&E<BR> Home Page</STRONG><BR>


<A HREF="commer.htm"><IMG SRC="images/combutn.gif" ALT="[Commercial]" WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=32 border=none></A><BR>


<IMG SRC="images/1resbutn.gif" ALT="[Residential]" WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=32 border=none><BR>


<A HREF="ite_bill.htm"><IMG SRC="images/billbutn.gif" ALT="[Billing]" WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=32 border=none></A><BR>


<A HREF="ite_hist.htm"><IMG SRC="images/hisbutn.gif" ALT="[History]" WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=32 border=none></A><BR>


</td><td><BR>


<IMG SRC="images/blineh9.gif" WIDTH=2 HEIGHT=180>


</td><td>


<table border=0><tr><td>


<IMG SRC="images/sphere.gif"></td><td>International Direct Dial</td></tr>


<tr><td>


<IMG SRC="images/sphere.gif"></td><td><A HREF="#econo">Econo Charge or Econo Plus Account</A></td></tr>


<tr><td>


<IMG SRC="images/sphere.gif"></td><td><A HREF="#foreign">Country Direct Service</A></td></tr>


<tr><td>


<IMG SRC="images/sphere.gif"></td><td><A HREF="#800">800 Services</A></td></tr>


<tr><td>


<IMG SRC="images/sphere.gif"></td><td><A HREF="#credit">International Credit Card Calling</A>


</td></tr></table>


</td></tr></table>





<CENTER><hr width=300 align=center>


<A HREF="mailto:genmgr@ite.net"><I>genmgr@ite.net</I></A></center>


<center><table border=0 width=520>


<td><BR><FONT SIZE=+2><CENTER><P>Local Telephone Account</CENTER></FONT><BR>To dial long distance charged to your telephone number. By dialing 011+, your telephone calls will be charged to the <STRONG>originating telephone number</STRONG> on Guam.</A><BR><BR>


 <STRONG><EM>Dial:</EM></STRONG> 011+ country code+area/city code+telephone number


<BR>





<FONT SIZE=+2><CENTER><A NAME="econo"><HR WIDTH=500 ALIGN=center SIZE=5></A><BR>Econo Charge or Econo Plus Account</CENTER></FONT><BR>


 Charge It! Thats the way to go in the 90s. By dialing 016+  calls will be charged to your <STRONG>IT&E/AT&T Econo Charge card or Econo Plus account</STRONG>. Each account is assigned an authorization code which is entered for every call made.  Billing identifies the account through this code permitting the user the flexibility for making calls from any telephone in Guam.<BR><BR><STRONG><EM>Dial:</EM></STRONG> 016+wait for voice prompt+country code+area/city code+telephone number+wait for voice prompt+econo charge number+4-digit pin number or Econo Plus number


<BR>


<FONT SIZE=+2><CENTER><A NAME="foreign"><HR WIDTH=500 ALIGN=center SIZE=5></A><BR>Country Direct Service</CENTER></FONT><BR>


 If you want to reach a country operator directly in the United States (AT&T), Australia (Telstra), Japan (KDD), Philippines (PLDT), Palau (PNCC), and Korea (DACOM), this simple prefix is available for users.</A><BR><BR>


<STRONG><EM>Dial:</EM></STRONG><STRONG>018+</STRONG><EM><STRONG>The Following Numbers...</Strong></EM><BR>
<UL>
<L1><STRONG>872</STRONG>-AT&T Direct (Voice Prompt)<BR>
<L1><STRONG>567</STRONG>-DACOM (Operator)<BR>
<L1><STRONG>576</STRONG>-KDD (Operator)<BR>
<L1><STRONG>533</STRONG>-KDD (Voice Prompt)<BR>
<L1><STRONG>581</STRONG>-Korea Telecom (Operator)<BR>
<L1><STRONG>582</STRONG>-Korea Telecom (Voice Prompt)<BR>
<L1><STRONG>744</STRONG>-PLDT Operator<BR>
<L1><STRONG>610</STRONG>-Australia (Telstra Voice Prompt)<BR>
</UL>

<BR>

<FONT SIZE=+2><CENTER><A NAME="800"><HR WIDTH=500 ALIGN=center SIZE=5></A><BR>800 Services</CENTER></FONT><BR><IMG SRC="images/blueball.gif"> International 800  <STRONG><EM>Dial:</EM></STRONG>01-800+ the number


<BR><BR><IMG SRC="images/blueball.gif"> Domestic 800 - Access to 800 services not included as International 800 by the vendors. This allows local callers full access to U.S. 800 services that are not included in the International Toll Free System <EM>at the incredible rate of only 50 cents per minute. </EM> <STRONG><EM>Dial:</EM></STRONG>01-880+ the number


<BR><BR><IMG SRC="images/blueball.gif"> Traveling 800<IMG ALIGN=right SRC="images/800.gif" HSPACE=10 ALT="[Traveling 800]"></CENTER></FONT><BR>


 As a service to our customers traveling to the Continental United States or Hawaii, calls to Guam or Saipan may be charged to an <STRONG>Econo Plus</STRONG> or <STRONG>Econo Charge</STRONG> card. Ideal for the college bound student. Just Dial 1-800-852-4826, wait for voice prompt, dial (671) or (670) + the Number. Wait for second voice prompt, enter either your Econo-Plus Authorization code or Econo-Charge number and 4-digit PIN.  All calls are charged to your account and appear on your monthly bill.<BR>


<BR><STRONG><EM>Dial: </EM></STRONG> 1-800-852-GUAM (4826)+wait for voice prompt+(671)or(670) telephone number+wait for voice prompt+7-digit econo plus authorization code or econo charge #+4-digit PIN<BR>





<FONT SIZE=+2><CENTER><A NAME="credit"><HR WIDTH=500 ALIGN=center SIZE=5></A><BR>International Direct Access Auto-Credit Card Calling (IDAC)</FONT></CENTER><BR>


This service allows Guam customers to <STRONG>call collect</STRONG> to the United States, Philippines, and Japan or call points served by IT&E and charge the call to the following credit cards:<BR><HR WIDTH=500 ALIGN=center SIZE=5></td></table></center>


