<STRONG>013+</STRONG> Operator assisted Collect,  Person to Person, Station to Station calls charged to an <STRONG>Econo Plus</STRONG> account or <STRONG>Econo Charge</STRONG> card are made by simply dialing 013 to reach the operator.</A><BR></td></table></center>

