<HEAD><TITLE>Calling Card Options</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000B8" VLINK="#000000" ALINK="#890000">
<FONT SIZE=+5><CENTER><EM>Calling Card Options</EM></CENTER></FONT>
<UL COMPACT><UL COMPACT><UL COMPACT><UL COMPACT><UL COMPACT><IMG SRC="images/blueball.gif"><A HREF="#plus">Econo Plus</A> - Econo Plus Charge Card<BR>
<IMG SRC="images/blueball.gif"><A HREF="#charge">Econo Charge</A> - Econo Charge Card<BR><IMG SRC="images/blueball.gif"><A HREF="#telcard">Telcard</A> - Prepaid Charge Card</UL></UL></UL></UL></UL>

<CENTER>
<hr width=300 align=center>
<A HREF="mailto:genmgr@ite.net"><I>genmgr@ite.net</I></A>
</center>
<center>
<table width=520 border=0>
<td width=50></td><td><A NAME="plus"></A><IMG SRC="images/econopl.jpg" VSPACE=20 ALT="[econo plus]" WIDTH=120 ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE><FONT SIZE=+1>Econo Plus Card</FONT><BR>
Affords the convenience of placing long distance telephone calls from any touch- tone phone on Guam and the CNMI, via a personal authorization code. While traveling in the U.S. Mainland or Hawaii, use our Traveling - 800 service. Call Guam or Saipan and charge the call to your Econo-Plus account.<BR>
<BR><A NAME="charge"><HR WIDTH=500 ALIGN=center SIZE=5></A>
<IMG SRC="images/econocd.gif" VSPACE=20 WIDTH=120 ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE><FONT SIZE=+1><STRONG> Econo Charge Card</STRONG></FONT></A><BR>
This joint AT&T/IT&E logo card, sometime referred to as the Power Card, allows calling to all locations served by AT&T/IT&E while maintaining the convenience of consolidated local billing. Application for a card  may  be made on Guam and processed within 10 working days. No pre-payment commitment is necessary.<BR>
<BR>

<A NAME="telcard"><HR WIDTH=500 ALIGN=center SIZE=5></A>
<IMG SRC="images/telcard1.gif" VSPACE=20 WIDTH=120 ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE><FONT SIZE=+1><STRONG> TelCards</FONT></STRONG><BR>
TelCards are pre-paid long distance calling cards extending users the capability of placing a debit call from any touch-tone telephone on Guam. These picturesque cards are available in $10, $20, and $50 denominations. Easy, user-friendly instructions are in English, Chamorro, Japanese, Tagalog,  or Korean.  Calls are made by simply dialing 646-3456 and following the voice instructions as prompted. IT&E TelCards are so easy to use that they make a great gift for special occasions like birthdays and anniversaries or are perfect island souvenirs. Purchase them at any of the IT&E offices on island.<BR>
<BR></td></table>
</center>
