<TITLE>Netcall Plus</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF" LINK="0000FF" VLINK="0000FF" >
</BODY>

<H1><b>IT&E introduces <FONT COLOR="400080"><b><i>'NetCall Plus'</i></b></FONT COLOR>, an innovative plan for internet users.</b></H1>

This is a new program that rewards <IMG SRC="images/talayalet.gif" ALT="Talaya 2000" ALIGN="absmiddle" BORDER=0> users with free bonus hours based on the volume of long distance calls per month that an IT&E customer makes.<br>

<H3><b>The Plan</b></H3>
<TABLE BORDER>
<th>Monthly Long Distance Bill with IT&E<br> (Net after discounts and without past due balance)</th><th>Bonus Time on Talaya 2000</th><tr>
<td><CENTER>$30.00-$49.99</CENTER></td><td><CENTER>One (1) hour</CENTER></td><tr>
<td><CENTER>$50.00-$99.99</CENTER></td><td><CENTER>Two (2) hours</CENTER></td><tr>
<td><CENTER>$100.00 or more</CENTER></td><td><CENTER>Four (4) hours</CENTER></td><tr>
</TABLE>
<br>

<H3><b>Eligibility Requirements</b></H3>
<UL>
<LI>All  IT&E residential long distance subscribers on Guam and CNMI.  
<LI>Limited to one Talaya account per telephone number or IT&E long distance account and both must be under the same name.
<LI>You must register...For your convenience <A HREF="http://talaya.ite.net/custsvc/netcall_plus.htm">click here</A> to register.

</UL>

<b><H3>Program Conditions</H3></b>
<p><UL>
<LI>Free bonus hours on <IMG SRC="images/talayalet.gif" ALT="Talaya 2000" ALIGN="absmiddle" BORDER=0> is specifically extended during the current month, provided the previous months long distance charges are paid in full by the due date.<br>
<LI>Unused bonus hours do not carry over to succeeding months.</UL><br>

<CENTER><BLINK><H3><A HREF="http://talaya.ite.net/custsvc/netcall_plus.htm">REGISTER NOW!</A></H3></BLINK></CENTER>

For more information please contact an IT&E or Talaya 2000 representative at 646-INET or <A HREF="mailto:talmktg@ite.net">email</A> us.

