</td><td width=10%></td><td valign=top width=65%><font color="#000000"><font size=4><strong>November Is</strong><em><strong> </strong></em></font></font><font color="#008080"><font size=4><em><strong>National Diabetes Month</strong></em></font></font><p>Each year the American Diabetes Association sponsors 
National Diabetes Month during November. This year the 
<em>Methodist Health Care System</em> is pleased to offer the 
following events and services to support people with diabetes 
and their family and friends. </p>
<ul>
<li><a href="walk.htm">Walk for the Cure</a> a major success !</li>
<li><a href="marathon.htm">Decision to Control Diabetes Pays Off for Marathon 
Hopeful</a></li>

<!-- <li>Free Diabetes <a href="openhouse.htm">Screening Exams</a></li>
<li><a href="openhouse.htm">Diabetes Expo</a> November 19, at the Methodist Dunn Tower Conference Center</li>-->

</ul>
<p>More than 16 million people are affected by diabetes, but half 
of these are unaware that they have the disease. To find out if 
you are are at risk for diabetes take the <a href="http://www.diabetes.org/ada/risktest.html">American Diabetes 
Association risk test. </a></p>
