<title>What's Ailing You?</title>
<BODY BGCOLOR="ffffff">
<center><font size=+1><img src=/methodist/icon/h-way.gif><br><h1><hr size=6><font size=+3><b>
What's Ailing You?</b></font><hr size=6></h1></font></center>

Welcome to the hallways of The Methodist Hospital.  Each year, tens of thousands of people from throughout the world find answers here.  Relief.  An end to suffering.  Countless others find the information, insight and training they need to maintain or improve their health.  <p>

Feel free to wander.  But please excuse the construction.  Were working hard to provide the kind of online hospital that will be useful to you.  Hopefully, these halls will lead to the information youre after.  If not, please let us know whats missing by filling out our <a href=/cgi-win/survey.exe>survey.</a><p>

