<title>Healthwatch</title><center><font size=+1>
<img src=health.jpg><br><h1><hr size=6><font size=+3>
<b>Health and Prevention Library</b></font><hr size=6></h1>
</center></font>
Welcome to Health Watch, The Methodist Hospitals growing cyber-library of health and wellness information.  We encourage you to explore our card catalog, whether youre looking for resources on a specific health issue or just poking around to see whats here.  So far, weve compiled a wide variety of information for these shelves and, unlike most libraries, the information you want is guaranteed to be at your fingertips.  You dont even have to keep your voice down.
<p>
Were working hard to fill our library with the kinds of health and wellness topics that you want to find.  If an issue that youre interested in is not on our shelves, let us know.  Well do our best to get it in stock.
<p>
