<BLOCKQUOTE>
  <P><FONT COLOR="#6666FF">Welcome to the <I><TT>The Journal,</TT></I> the
  magazine of The Methodist Health Care System. The print version of this
  magazine is published three times each year. We hope you find some useful
  and interesting information here and we welcome your comments. For more
  information about this publication go to </FONT><A HREF="masthead.html">Masthead.
  </A>
<P>
<FONT COLOR="ffffff">
<CENTER>Missed the previous issue? We have it On-Line.<BR>
<A HREF="../magazine/34/index.html">VOLUME 34 NUMBER 2, 1995</A><BR>
<A HREF="../magazine/35/index.html">VOLUME 35 NUMBER 1, 1996</A><BR>
</CENTER>
</FONT>
