<title>Managing your Care</title>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><!--body background=/methodist/manage/managbg.jpg>
<center>
<img src=manage.jpg>
</center>


<p>
Welcome to Managing your Care, The Methodist Hospital's online resource for information about managed care:  how it works, how to enroll in a plan and how to choose a plan that offers the health care services that are important to you.
<p>
<a href=plans.htm>
<img src=i-plans.gif align=middle> PLANS</a><br>
If you're one of the millions of Houston area residents participating in a managed care plan, we have great news!  The Methodist Hospital is now offering its world-famous services to members of a number of <a href=plans.htm>managed care plans</a> in and around our fair city, including the Cigna, Cigna Select and PruCare health maintenance organizations (HMOs).
<p>
<a href=choices.htm>
<img src=i-choice.gif align=middle> CHOICES</a><br>
Thinking about joining a managed care plan?  How can you be sure you'll receive the best care available?  When your employer has <a href=choices.htm>open enrollment</a>, take advantage of the chance to be sure your health plan gives you access to the best health care. Insist 
on Methodist!
<p>
<a href=info.htm>
<img src=i-info.gif align=middle> INFO</a><br>
Don't know much about managed care? <a href=info.htm> Click here</a> to find a brief explanation as well as a managed care glossary.  Once you learn more about it, you may find that managed care is your best health care option.


<p><hr size=4></font><center><b>
<A HREF="/~imagemap/mhsmall"><IMG SRC="/methodist/icon/m-menu.gif" ISMAP border=0></a>
