<title>Methodist Search Tool</title>
<center><img src=/methodist/search/search.gif></center>
<p>You can use this form to search for documents on the Methodist Hospital Server.You can use 'and' and 'or' between your keywords;'and' applies by default.<br><form method=GET action="/cgi-dos/webfind.exe">Type your keywords here:<input name=keywords size=50><p><input type=submit value="Find Documents"><input type=reset value="Clear"></form>

<h3>
<hr size=6>The following search tools will allow you to search the 
Internet for more information </h3>
 
<DL>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.cs.indiana.edu/aliweb/search"><B>Aliweb</B></A> 
