<title>Mission</title>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<center><font size=+1>
<img src=/methodist/about/about.gif><br>
<h1><hr size=6><font size=+3><b>Mission of The Methodist Hospital System</b></font><hr size=6></h1>
</font>
</center>

<font size=+2>T</font>o provide high quality, 
cost effective health care that delivers the best value to the people we serve in a 
spiritual environment of caring through an integrated delivery and financing system 
in association with internationally recognized teaching and research.

<hr size=4></font><center><b><A HREF="/~imagemap/mhsmall"><IMG SRC="/methodist/icon/m-menu.gif" ISMAP border=0></a>
<p align=center>| <a href="http://www.methodisthealth.com/about/index.html">Get To Know Us</a> | <a href="http://www.methodisthealth.com/ailing/index.html">What's Ailing You</a> | <a href="http://www.methodisthealth.com/health/index.html">Health Watch</a> | <a href="http://www.methodisthealth.com/magazine/index.html">Page Turners</a> |<br>
